<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich von Wiesenthau, Vogt von Wernfels</head><p>Der Rat bittet nach Klage des Heinz Steinlinger, Pfleger der siechen Frauen zu St. Johannis bei Nürnberg, den Armmann Hermann Schmidt von Beerbach zu sichern.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_74" id="36v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_74_r2l1"><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von vviſentawe / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r2l2">vogt cʒu vverdenfels / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_74_r2l3">Lieber <expan>vviſentaw<ex>er</ex></expan> / vns hat fürgelegt Heintʒ <expan>Steinling<ex>er</ex></expan> vnſer <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> / pfleger der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r2l4">ſiehen frawen cʒu ſant Johans beÿ vns / wie Jm <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> Smÿdt von perbach / <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r2l5">ſichen Armman geklagt hab / 
<del rend="strikethrough">wie </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_74_line_1573048858612_44">daʒ </ab></add> er vor euch vnſicher ſeÿ / <expan>Rog<ex>amus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr Jn <expan>ſich<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r2l6">wöllet auf frewntlich recht / das wöllen etc / het Jr dann cʒu <expan>demſelbe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> Smÿdt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r2l7">icht cʒu ſprechen / darv̈mb ſo wil 
<del rend="strikethrough">ent </del> der <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>e</ex></expan> vnſer Burger ew / <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> ſchein = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r2l8">boten mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> vollen gewalt / von Jm vnuertʒogen <expan>ſlewnig<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> helffen / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r2l9">vvenn er des ermant wirt / vnd laſʒt vns des ewr <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider wiſʒen / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r2l10"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> feria <expan>S<ex>e</ex>c<ex>un</ex>da</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Anthonj / Anno etc decimo $ $ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_74" id="36v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Wisentawe, vogt czu Werdenfels </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber <expan>Wisentaw<ex>er</ex></expan>, uns hat fürgelegt Heincz
                                <expan>Steinling<ex>er</ex></expan>, unser
                            <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, pfleger der siehen frawen czu sant
                        Johans bey uns, wie im <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> Smydt von Perbach,
                                <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sichen armman, geklagt hab,
                            <add>daz</add> er vor euch unsicher sey.
                        <expan>Rog<ex>amus</ex></expan>, daz ir in <expan>sich<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        wöllet auf frewntlich recht, das wöllen etc. Het ir dann czu
                                <expan>demselbe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> Smydt icht czu sprechen, darümb so wil der
                                <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>e</ex></expan> unser burger ew
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> scheinboten mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
                        vollen gewalt von im unverczogen <expan>slewnig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> helffen, wenn er des ermant wirt; und laszt uns
                        des ewr <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider wiszen. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
                        feria <expan>s<ex>e</ex>c<ex>un</ex>da</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Anthoni anno etc. decimo.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
